from tensorflow.python.client import device_lib

def get_available_gpus():
    local_device_protos = device_lib.list_local_devices()
    return [x.name for x in local_device_protos if x.device_type == 'GPU']

In [13]:
alexnet = Sequential()
# 1 convo layer
alexnet.add(Conv2D(filters= 96,input_shape = IMAGE_SIZE +[3],kernel_size = (11,11),strides = (4,4),padding = 'valid'))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))

# maxpool
alexnet.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size=(3,3),strides = (2,2),padding = 'valid'))

#2 convo layer
alexnet.add(Conv2D(filters= 256,kernel_size = (5,5),strides = (1,1),padding = 'valid'))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))

#maxpool
alexnet.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size=(3,3),strides = (2,2),padding = 'valid'))

#3 convo layer
alexnet.add(Conv2D(filters= 384,kernel_size = (3,3),strides = (1,1),padding = 'valid'))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))

#4 convo layer
alexnet.add(Conv2D(filters= 384,kernel_size = (3,3),strides = (1,1),padding = 'valid'))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))

#5 convo layer
alexnet.add(Conv2D(filters= 256,kernel_size = (3,3),strides = (1,1),padding = 'valid'))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))
#maxpool
alexnet.add(MaxPooling2D(pool_size=(3,3),strides = (2,2),padding = 'valid'))
#passing it to fullty connected layer
alexnet.add(Flatten())
#1 fully connected layer
alexnet.add(Dense(4096,input_shape = (224*224*3,)))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))
#add dropout
alexnet.add(Dropout(0.5))

#2 fully connected layer
alexnet.add(Dense(4096))
alexnet.add(Activation('relu'))
#add dropout
alexnet.add(Dropout(0.5))
